                    "elements": [
                        {
                            "id": "b1f7b5e",
                            "settings": {
                                "tabs": [
                                    {
                                        "tab_title": "Evente looks great  -  what is it?",
                                        "_id": "f172c9e",
                                        "accordion_tab_default_active": "yes",
                                        "accordion_tab_title_icon": {
                                            "value": "far fa-plus-square",
                                            "library": "fa-regular"
                                        },
                                        "accordion_tab_title_icon_collapse": {
                                            "value": "far fa-minus-square",
                                            "library": "fa-regular"
                                        },
                                        "single_tab_title_bg_color_show": "",
                                        "accordion_content": "<p>Evente is a virtual space where you and your remote team can work and hang out together. Evente makes spending time with your remote team fun &amp; productive.</p>"
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "tab_title": "Is my data secure with Tell Desk?",
                                        "accordion_tab_default_active": "",
                                        "accordion_tab_title_icon": {
                                            "value": "far fa-plus-square",
                                            "library": "fa-regular"
                                        },
                                        "accordion_tab_title_icon_collapse": {
                                            "value": "far fa-minus-square",
                                            "library": "fa-regular"
                                        },
                                        "single_tab_title_bg_color_show": "",
                                        "accordion_content": "<p>Absolutely. We use enterprise-grade encryption, role-based access, and regular security audits to ensure your data is always protected. Tell Desk is also GDPR-compliant.</p>",
                                        "_id": "583abc9"
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "tab_title": "How does the pricing model work?",
                                        "accordion_tab_default_active": "",
                                        "accordion_tab_title_icon": {
                                            "value": "far fa-plus-square",
                                            "library": "fa-regular"
                                        },
                                        "accordion_tab_title_icon_collapse": {
                                            "value": "far fa-minus-square",
                                            "library": "fa-regular"
                                        },
                                        "single_tab_title_bg_color_show": "",
                                        "accordion_content": "<p>Tell Desk offers a flexible subscription model. You can choose between monthly or annual billing, with different plans tailored for startups, growing businesses, and enterprises. Custom pricing is also available for larger teams.</p>",
                                        "_id": "eb90de7"
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "tab_title": "Can my team collaborate on Tell Desk in real-time?",
                                        "accordion_tab_default_active": "",
                                        "accordion_tab_title_icon": {
                                            "value": "far fa-plus-square",
                                            "library": "fa-regular"
                                        },
                                        "accordion_tab_title_icon_collapse": {
                                            "value": "far fa-minus-square",
                                            "library": "fa-regular"
                                        },
                                        "single_tab_title_bg_color_show": "",
                                        "accordion_content": "<p>Yes! Multiple users can collaborate in real-time, track progress, and assign tasks. You\u2019ll always have visibility into who is working on what, without messy back-and-forth emails.</p>",
                                        "_id": "5363268"
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "tab_title": "What kind of support does Tell Desk provide?",
                                        "accordion_tab_default_active": "",
                                        "accordion_tab_title_icon": {
                                            "value": "far fa-plus-square",
                                            "library": "fa-regular"
                                        },
                                        "accordion_tab_title_icon_collapse": {
                                            "value": "far fa-minus-square",
                                            "library": "fa-regular"
                                        },
                                        "single_tab_title_bg_color_show": "",
                                        "accordion_content": "<p>We offer 24/7 email support, live chat during business hours, and a knowledge base with step-by-step guides. Premium plans include dedicated account managers.</p>",
                                        "_id": "a2ee3e4"
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "tab_title": "Can I try Tell Desk before purchasing?",
                                        "accordion_tab_default_active": "",
                                        "accordion_tab_title_icon": {
                                            "value": "far fa-plus-square",
                                            "library": "fa-regular"
                                        },
                                        "accordion_tab_title_icon_collapse": {
                                            "value": "far fa-minus-square",
                                            "library": "fa-regular"
                                        },
                                        "single_tab_title_bg_color_show": "",
                                        "accordion_content": "<p>Yes, we offer a 14-day free trial with full access to all features\u2014no credit card required. This way, you can explore Tell Desk and see if it\u2019s the right fit for your team</p>",
                                        "_id": "ff85b22"
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "tab_title": "How do I get started with Tell Desk?",
                                        "accordion_tab_default_active": "",
                                        "accordion_tab_title_icon": {
                                            "value": "far fa-plus-square",
                                            "library": "fa-regular"
                                        },
                                        "accordion_tab_title_icon_collapse": {
                                            "value": "far fa-minus-square",
                                            "library": "fa-regular"
                                        },
                                        "single_tab_title_bg_color_show": "",
                                        "accordion_content": "<p>Getting started is simple. Sign up on our website, customize your workspace, and invite your team. Our onboarding wizard will guide you through the setup in under 10 minutes.</p>",
                                        "_id": "e9944f6"
                                    }
                                ],
